        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're wielding a weapon that deals physical damage.</p><hr /><p>You coat your weapon or its ammunition in your toxic stomach fluids, which remain potent until the end of your next turn. The next time you successfully Strike a creature with the required weapon within the duration, if the Strike deals damage, you deal an additional 1d4 poison damage to the target. At 3rd level and every 2 levels thereafter, this damage increases by 1d4.</p>"
